text: Fejervarya kawamurai is a species of frog in the family Dicroglossidae. It is endemic to Taiwan, Japan (Ryukyu Islands and Honshu), and China. It belongs to the Fejervarya limnocharis species complex. ==Sources== * Djong, Matsui, Kuramoto, Nishioka & Sumida, 2011 : A new species of the Fejervarya limnocharis complex from Japan (Anura, Dicroglossidae). title: Fejervarya kawamurai
